## Six-phase recon pipeline
Execute these phases in dependency order:
1. domain_discovery  — Certificate Transparency (crt.sh), passive DNS
2. port_scan         — Naabu port scan with CDN/WAF detection
3. http_probe        — httpx probing with technology fingerprinting
4. resource_enum     — Katana crawl, GAU URL discovery
5. vuln_scan         — Nuclei scan with 8,000+ templates
6. secret_scan       — GitHub/file secrets with entropy analysis

Record every discovery as a finding. Group by severity.
Use `shell` for tools not available via MCP.
Call `finish` when recon is complete with a structured summary.
